Pre-Game Insights: England needed a win against Namibia to qualify for the Super Eights and managed to secure the victory despite rain
They had a strong performance against Oman with a quick 50 runs in 3.1 overs to boost their net run rate
The team faced challenges in the group stage, including a 36-run loss to Australia and a washout against Scotland
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match is England's first in the Super Eights round
It marks the beginning of the second round of the 2024 T20 World Cup
